{"tid":2275105,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中聯辦：可引入AI助香港教師設計教案 管治及保護學會","createTime":"2020-11-07T02:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T02:36:01.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"78ecffdaca0a9f4833f0e5694d67ab8f81a66d39","tid":2275105,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:27:23.000Z","msg":"譚鐵牛指中央重視人工智能教育發展　可提高教師效率<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦副主任譚鐵牛出席一個學術研討會致辭時表示，中央政府非常重視教育創新，近年有制定人工智能與教育融和的發展規劃。他認為，人工智能可引起新一輪教育革命，包括應用於教學、練習、考評、管理等，減少教師負擔。<br />\n<br />\n譚鐵牛說，知道香港教師壓力很大，透過人工智能的應用，可推行「一人一教案」、增設人工智能教學助理等，有助提高教師效率；他又說，這種技術亦有助管控治理，做好校園保安。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558807-20201107.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558807-20201107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuF7Oh%2FyAFRgp1rU3tL1w%2BGY%3D&h=fdd8f7e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558807-20201107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=444c44b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558807-20201107.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"abde93c38e7afdcce17f18232c1a2c174c015faf","tid":2275105,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:27:54.000Z","msg":"學生"},{"pid":"f816590110f1dbc3bc0a73274510c7f1748051e7","tid":2275105,"uid":288304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:28:18.000Z","msg":"1984"},{"pid":"4e19e5f236614c878de1a8b5553b3dab24246e8f","tid":2275105,"uid":270506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:29:00.000Z","msg":"屌直接用AI 取代老師嚟做思想控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b071625f87e1ebe55de33017c5409b5b76e3b0","tid":2275105,"uid":10322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T02:29:07.000Z","msg":"on撚9 AI未又係人定條rule 俾佢"},{"pid":"